Once again :-))) :

Do not copy whole folder called Crack to directory where you installed the game just exe file (in every Crack folder you have three files: file id, SSlEvIN.nfo and exe file(the one with icon exactly the same as game original))and when asked do you want to replace existing file with this one click Yes. Thats it. :-)))

Bsically.... The Executible file found in the crack folder should be copied to the game installation folder found in c:\program files\GAME NAME

"GAME NAME" would be the folder name of the game.....

eg.   c:\program files\legobot

some games are from yahoo.....  those are found  in c:\program files\yahoo games\GAME NAME

Hope this helps the confusion, its pretty straight forward.....
